        <title>Use PowerPoint making a Simple ring color circle</title>
        <link>https://hyruo.com/en/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 07 May 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://hyruo.com/en/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/m-3-jpg-1.webp" alt="Featured image of post Use PowerPoint making a Simple ring color circle" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;When watching some PPT tutorials, I found that many designs are more classic, so I tried to imitate them. What I imitated tonight is an arc-shaped circular color circle. Since the process is a bit cumbersome, I made a simple tutorial.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2.gif&#34;
	width=&#34;493&#34;
	height=&#34;444&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2_hu09ca8dd848172c8cba958ab3648412d4_215696_480x0_resize_box_1.gif 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2_hu09ca8dd848172c8cba958ab3648412d4_215696_1024x0_resize_box_1.gif 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;111&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;266px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;renderings&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;production-process&#34;&gt;Production process:
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM1-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;807&#34;
	height=&#34;451&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM1-jpg_hu121022e9a80625f7bad4cf216fda03e1_10310_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM1-jpg_hu121022e9a80625f7bad4cf216fda03e1_10310_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;178&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;429px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;first-step&#34;&gt;first step
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since the imitation is a 12-segment ring, each segment is 30 degrees. For accurate realization, it needs to be calibrated with the help of a triangle. What needs to be paid attention to when making an isosceles triangle is to ensure that the apex is on the midline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm2-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;802&#34;
	height=&#34;454&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm2-jpg_hu5872a0339921d82abc4cec406e7c9dc0_8816_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm2-jpg_hu5872a0339921d82abc4cec406e7c9dc0_8816_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;176&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;423px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;second-step&#34;&gt;second step
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The center of the hollow arc needs to be carefully calibrated, otherwise the next step will be difficult to do well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm3-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;807&#34;
	height=&#34;464&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm3-jpg_hu6c9eec8d93764d885119d83ca7e1bba3_10180_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm3-jpg_hu6c9eec8d93764d885119d83ca7e1bba3_10180_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;173&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;417px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;third-step&#34;&gt;third step
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Duplicate the combination three times to form a circle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm4-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;802&#34;
	height=&#34;463&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm4-jpg_hu573f6db3fa063211f951c69fcf2ef208_9968_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/mm4-jpg_hu573f6db3fa063211f951c69fcf2ef208_9968_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;173&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;415px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-fourth-step&#34;&gt;the fourth step
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;When scaling the graphics, you need to hold down shift to ensure no deformation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM-2-1024x582.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;582&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM-2-1024x582_hub4867217966623bc63282766f1fa5b25_20386_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/MM-2-1024x582_hub4867217966623bc63282766f1fa5b25_20386_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;175&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;422px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2c-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;849&#34;
	height=&#34;479&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2c-jpg_hu053b8b7c063350075fe07abc0e36acf3_9982_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2c-jpg_hu053b8b7c063350075fe07abc0e36acf3_9982_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;425px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-fifth-step&#34;&gt;the fifth step
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cancel all graphic combinations, then combine the opposite hollow arcs, and set the gyro emphasis animation. After animating the 6 pairs of hollow arcs according to the timing, insert and add the exit effect appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2b-jpg.webp&#34;
	width=&#34;852&#34;
	height=&#34;462&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2b-jpg_hu9aaea839f18bbc64d197193df898fa84_19176_480x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/use-powerpoint-making-a-simple-ring-color-circle/images/2b-jpg_hu9aaea839f18bbc64d197193df898fa84_19176_1024x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;184&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;442px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;step-six&#34;&gt;step six
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Setting animations of multiple color circles at the same time requires a lot of reliance on animation brushes. The process is extremely cumbersome (the total number of animations reaches an astonishing 150), but the effect is also remarkable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
